{
  "stem": "12053.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was very difficult, to keep the continuity.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the brochure, more than this book even, results in ALL people getting to know each other all around the world.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We've got people-- and at the actual reunion, I mean, you can't imagine what it was like.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People describe it as a unique event.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They have never experienced anything like it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "IT ran for two days in the Harrow Leisure Center. 1,000 people from worldwide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People just say, you were at the reunion?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was-- you know, it's the people who were and the people who weren't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- it was something really special.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first day we sat at tables of origin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, we had 20 tables from Vienna. 200 people from Vienna came. 200 people from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tables with Munich, with Frankfurt, with-- and the little-- people from little towns, they had several little town names.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was absolutely-- I myself didn't really realize what was going on so much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was like the sort of the fairy on the-- on the Christmas tree, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or like the bride at the wedding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You sit at the head table, you don't know what goes on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the feedback was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We've got our own reunion film.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We've got our video.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The BBC made films.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The BBC made film, They made, They made-- the German crew sent-- the Germans sent a film crew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most wonderful film they made, called [SPEAKING GERMAN], as they were not allowed to be Germans anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they like long sentences.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was also a wonderful film.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One of the best I've ever seen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were very well received by the crowd.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were very surprised how well received they were by the Kinder.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
